Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: George Aiken of Vermont
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xfrr
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Dec 1984
An upright man - in his walk, and his ways. Remembering Senator George D. Aiken, the politician who could never be bought. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less